data.description: This 4 bedroom, den, 2 bathroom Jupiter Farms home offers the perfect canvas for creating your dream home in a serene and peaceful setting on 1.13 acres. Enjoy a beautifully updated exterior with a classic style and large yard with a covered patio. Offering 1,581 sq. ft. under air, with great features making it a perfect home in need of some updates for you to make it all your own. The possibilities are endless. Mature trees surround this home making it private and quiet, yet easily accessible to grocery stores, restaurants and highways. 2013 Metal roof, 2016 flat roof, 2012 Nordyne a/c, impact windows & front door, 12x24 shed, 2023 sod
